description: City- Medford, OR325 S Riverside Ave, Medford Oregon, 97501Ooblies Artisan Waffles is the perfect combination of waffle meets sandwich. Our waffle has a Light crispy crunch, the fluffiness of a cloud and a buttery flavor; it’s perfect for breakfast, lunch, dinner and even those late night cravings. For a savory experience try our Buttermilk Fried Chicken, Zesty Turkey Club, or Hot Pastrami. If you have a sweet tooth, our Nutella Sensation, S’more’s, or Berry Delightful is sure to satisfy. Sweet or savory, it doesn't matter because Happiness is inside every waffle! Some may call us mad, some may call us genius, but we just call ourselves Wafflers of Awesomeness!www.ooblie.com
